---
title: 'When Does More Context Make an AI Worse?'
date: '2026-07-11'
description: 'Agents should support fluid conversation and structured workspaces without making users understand the context machinery that keeps either one reliable.'
tags: ['ai', 'agents', 'engineering']
pillar: 'agentic-stack'
